<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1118505">在『真・女神転生』中，机械改造/サイバーウェア有着三层含义。其一便是将除大脑之外的部分全部义体化的赛博格/サイボーグ（cyborg）。角色觉醒了职业“赛博格”的话便意味着曾一度迎来肉体的死亡，其后作为赛博格而重生。<br><br><strong><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size">赛博格/サイボーグ</span></strong><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: blue;" class="bbc_color">※特殊</span></span><br><br><em>接受了全身义体化的赛博格战士。它们作为弥赛亚教会或高科技企业的先锋被投入到了和恶魔的战斗当中</em><br><br><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">觉醒关键词</span></strong><br>•肉体之死<br>•改造手术<br>•和高科技企业的交易<br><br><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">能力值</span></strong><br>力 3 魔 1 体 1 速 4 运 1<br><br><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">道具</span></strong><br>人造义体<br><br><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">风格</span></strong><br>射击（枪械）/守护者<br><br><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">技能</span></strong><br>L1：反射神经强化&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;L27：电子系追加技能<br>L3：分析&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; L33：追加射击威力<br>L7：回避强化&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;L37：妥当处理<br>L13：追加先攻值&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; L43：特攻<br>L17：一分活泉&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;L47：物理耐性<br>L23：电子系追加技能&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; L51：电子系追加技能<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">pc终于能合理地自爆了 <img src="/bbs/Smileys/converted/Lem06.GIF" alt="&#58;em006" title="&#58;em006" border="0" class="smiley"/></div></div></div></div>
